Package: ggmagnify
Title: Create a Magnified Inset of Part of a "ggplot" Object
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: David Hugh-Jones, ggplot2 team
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Hugh-Jones", , "davidhughjones@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates a magnified inset of a ggplot, with projection lines and
  borders around the target area and inset, plus optional shadow.
